        "Peak paper \"Variable Stiffness Actuators: Review on Design and Components\" (2015, 432 cites) — fell in late career.",
        "68 likely students — top: Emanuele Guglielmino(2009~, we last-author on 19), Petar Kormushev(2010~, we last-author on 16), Matteo Laffranchi(2009~, we last-author on 14)."
